1 D. The Oklahoma Tax Commission shall promulgate rules to
2 implement the provisions of this section which shall contain a
3 specific list of nonrecurring adoption expenses which may be
4 presumed to qualify for the tax credit. The Tax Commission shall
5 prescribe necessary requirements for verification.
6 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective January 1, 2026.
